title: Eddie Vedder - Walks On His Own (live solo)
description:
A collection of solo performances by Eddie Vedder of Pearl Jam.  All songs are excellent quality and crowd noise is edited to sound kinda like a complete live show.   Includes songs written by Vedder and covers by The Who, Cat Stevens, Tom Waits, Bruce Springsteen, Tom Petty, The Beatles and others. A little something I threw together a few months ago...
